# EV4 Architect

Project Gate integration is planned; the verifier is not implemented.

Repository role: produce the approved architecture handoff while preserving selected-candidate identity, approved structure, class intent, forbidden work, unknowns, and missing evidence.

```text
Architect output → EV4 Project Gate
accepted → CE Input Package
not accepted → Architect correction package
```

EV4 Project Gate checks the handoff with this repository's official contracts. Architect remains authoritative for Architect schemas, validators, fixtures, and semantics. Project Gate does not create missing architecture facts or prove constructability.

See `README.md` for the full approved workflow.
